FT  12 JAN 93 / Proposals for education budgets
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
PROPOSALS for greater delegation of council education budgets to schools
were announced yesterday. From April 1995 councils will be required to
delegate 90 per cent of their schools budget, up from 85 per cent. Special
schools will receive fully delegated budgets from 1996.
